# PRODIGY_WD_01 — Weather App

## 📌 Task Details

*Track:* Web Development (PRODIGY_WD)  
*Task Number:* 01 — Weather App  
*Description:*  
A beautiful weather dashboard that fetches real-time weather data using OpenWeatherMap API. Features:
- City search
- Current location
- 5-day forecast
- Dark mode toggle
- Fully responsive design

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS (with Dark Mode)
- Vanilla JavaScript
- OpenWeatherMap API

## 🌐 Live Link

[View the app here](https://shalini1920.github.io/PRODIGY_WD_01/)

## 📂 How to run

1. Clone this repo
2. Open index.html with Live Server

